1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:55,520
[Crossroad Bistro]

3
00:01:55,600 --> 00:02:00,240
[Ep15]

4
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,040
She must be really scared.

5
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,960
I heard her shouting in the car from a distance.

6
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,320
When she sat next to me,

7
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:07,090
I couldn't even hear the engine.

8
00:02:07,090 --> 00:02:07,800
If I didn't know,

9
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,360
I'd have thought you're killing someone.

10
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,000
Have a can of War Horse.

11
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:13,640
Get more energy.

12
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,480
Alright.

13
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:15,280
Thanks, Jun.

14
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:17,960
Yu Songyang.

15
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:20,440
I need to pick up my bag from your car.

16
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,680
I have to go back.

17
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,800
Stay for longer and have fun.

18
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,570
Excuse me.

19
00:02:23,570 --> 00:02:24,250
I've got stuff to do.

20
00:02:24,250 --> 00:02:24,880
I'll be off.

21
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:25,579
See you next time.

22
00:02:25,579 --> 00:02:26,360
Bye-bye.

23
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,160
That's quick.

24
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:28,640
Xue.

25
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,360
What's the problem?

26
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:33,160
I'm gonna kill Dai Xiaoyu when I go back.

27
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,280
She made up with Peng Pai.

28
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:42,200
Would you feel that I'm a big loser?

29
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:44,600
No.

30
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,600
How do you live

31
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,480
and who do you live with

32
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:47,960
are totally up to you.

33
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:52,040
I know I let you down a lot.

34
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:57,680
I do think you should be better than this.

35
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:59,680
I was just thinking

36
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:02,560
that I'm 30 now.

37
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:04,800
I can't act on impulse anymore.

38
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,800
It's time I have a stable life.

39
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,720
Xiaoyu,

40
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,400
do you think that you might have

41
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,840
misunderstood the meaning of stability?

42
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,240
A life without worries

43
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,160
counts as stable, right?

44
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,920
Are you sure a life with someone like him

45
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,040
is without worries?

46
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,040
Never mind.

47
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,280
Let's not talk about this.

48
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,000
Tell me your plans for the next step.

49
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,240
I plan to go back

50
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,600
to Norway with him.

51
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:34,760
If so,

52
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:35,840
I can return your investment.

53
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,760
But I don't want that.

54
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:39,920
Do you want to kick me out?

55
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:43,079
The thing is,

56
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:44,800
I prefer to make things clear.

57
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,880
We have been friends.

58
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:47,680
I won't kick anyone out without reason.

59
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,120
But you understand

60
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:51,960
that I bit your boyfriend's head off.

61
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,960
I'm afraid I won't be able to talk to him again.

62
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,640
Also, I do not wish to see him again.

63
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,520
If this continues,

64
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,240
it would be difficult

65
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,880
to keep being your friend.

66
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,560
I understand.

67
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,840
I don't want to go back to Norway any soon.

68
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,080
Also, I don't want to

69
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,320
quit the job Chai Yong gave me.

70
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:17,040
That's my career, after all.

71
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,880
Even if I marry him,

72
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,440
I won't be so dependent

73
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:22,560
on him like before.

74
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,680
I respect all your decisions.

75
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,440
If you're willing to keep cooperating,

76
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,520
I'm fine with that.

77
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,360
There is only one thing.

78
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,000
Never let him

79
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:34,880
come to this place again

80
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,480
in case he and I meet and both get embarrassed.

81
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,159
You're so calm.

82
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:42,520
It scares me a bit.

83
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,920
I'd rather you scolded me.

84
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,560
Never mind.

85
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,880
I can't force you

86
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,280
to live the way I want you to live.

87
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,640
As long as you're happy, it's good.

88
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,440
I just don't want

89
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,400
to let this matter

90
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,360
affect our relationship.

91
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:01,560
My opinion remains the same.

92
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,120
We can still be partners.

93
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,920
But as friends,

94
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,880
our relationship will be difficult to stay the same.

95
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,640
Alright.

96
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:14,920
I'll be off.

97
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,600
Chai will host a dinner here tomorrow,

98
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:19,160
but I won't be able to come.

99
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,600
No problem. Tell Feng Xi about it.

100
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:22,880
OK.

101
00:05:29,460 --> 00:05:31,440
Leave the private room to Mr. Chai tomorrow evening.

102
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:32,560
Sure.

103
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,640
Are you alright?

104
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:37,360
I'm fine.

105
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,640
How about you?

106
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,600
I'm good.

107
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,760
I'll get used to it soon.

108
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:45,840
I'll be off, then.

109
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,640
I have things to do tonight and won't be here.

110
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,040
Don't worry.

111
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:08,120
How can I not worry when seeing you like this?

112
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:14,160
Have you contacted him in the past few days?

113
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,640
No.

114
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:19,080
Why do I feel Xiaoyu doesn't look right, either?

115
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,080
What's the matter with her?

116
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:21,080
You are the same.

117
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,920
Both of you keep me worrying.

118
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,360
Hello.

119
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,240
Hello, Dai.

120
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,080
When will you come today?

121
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:47,360
But didn't we agree that I'll take photos of you today?

122
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,040
Sorry.

123
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,520
I forgot about it.

124
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,240
Come here if you don't have things to do.

125
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,600
I'm alone today, anyways.

126
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,880
Come any time.

127
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,680
Alright. I'll go there.

128
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,720
But I can't take photos today.

129
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,320
I have something to tell you.

130
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,360
Alright.

131
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,080
Dai.

132
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:17,240
There's one thing that I'm actually

133
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,200
better at compared with him.

134
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,240
You're more decisive when it comes to me.

135
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:25,080
I really don't want to waste your time.

136
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,080
Have you ever liked me?

137
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,200
I admit

138
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,720
that I feel happier with you

139
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,600
than when I'm with him.

140
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,600
But...

141
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,560
But you feel that with me,

142
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,680
you don't feel safe.

143
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,640
I realized it the other day when we

144
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,360
bought the video camera.

145
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,280
Indeed,

146
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,960
I don't have much of a plan.

147
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,880
I spend more than I earn

148
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,160
and haven't managed to save much.

149
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,360
But I can feel I have a bright future.

150
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,280
I know.

151
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,440
But men and women are different.

152
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,400
I'm already 30 now.

153
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:11,960
So what?

154
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,680
Are you half-dead?

155
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,320
You're only 30

156
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:18,400
and you want to live a life like a 60-year-old.

157
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,920
Do you think that's a stable life?

158
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:22,840
Liu.

159
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:26,880
I'm sorry.

160
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:35,600
You don't need to feel sorry.

161
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,960
I like you

162
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,039
from the bottom of my heart.

163
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:42,280
You refuse me

164
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,760
from the bottom of your heart, too.

165
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,160
Cheers, Dai.

166
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:49,440
We can still be friends, right?

167
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:51,680
Of course,

168
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,600
as long as you want to.

169
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:55,520
I do.

170
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,640
Wish you happiness.

171
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:00,760
Wish you happiness, too.

172
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,880
I've felt bad enough today.

173
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:09,520
Even you scold me.

174
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:12,960
I know what I did is unfair to Liu Liangzhou.

175
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,800
But that's what I think.

176
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,000
I just want to have a stable life.

177
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,040
What's wrong with it?

178
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:19,440
Sis.

179
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,320
Don't get angry at me.

180
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,840
I don't want to educate you

181
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,920
or stop you from having a happy life.

182
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,440
I just feel it's not good enough for you.

183
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,520
I also feel Liu is wronged.

184
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:29,440
Alright?

185
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:31,000
I will be the one to decide

186
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,920
if it's good enough for me.

187
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,320
If you feel for him so much,

188
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,720
use all resources you have

189
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,800
and find someone else for him.

190
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:37,520
You're right.

191
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:38,960
I really have to fill up

192
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,080
the hole you left in Liu.

193
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:43,000
Otherwise, I fear he will die for love.

194
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,200
That's too much.

195
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:46,080
When I left today,

196
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,360
he looked quite normal.

197
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:49,800
He was emotionally stable.

198
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:44,600
The movie starts at 6:00.

199
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,160
Don't be late.

200
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:53,440
The plans have changed.

201
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,320
6:30.

202
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:56,160
I'll meet you at the private room in Crossroad Bistro.

203
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:58,000
What else have you messed up?

204
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:05,040
I'm planning to introduce a girl to Liu Liangzhou.

205
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,760
You have to work with me.

206
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:07,440
I have to go.

207
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,880
I've arrived at Liu's place.

208
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:19,960
You're a proper photographer and an artist.

209
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:22,320
It's just a small setback, and you're already half dead.

210
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:23,560
I'm so disappointed.

211
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:24,200
I mean it.

212
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,540
Stop that.

213
00:11:26,540 --> 00:11:28,480
You won't understand unless you experience it.

214
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,880
Listen, Liu.

215
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,440
You have only two choices.

216
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:32,280
First,

217
00:11:32,560 --> 00:11:33,720
cross your fingers every day

218
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:35,680
and hope that my sis and Peng Pai break up again.

219
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:36,320
Second,

220
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,120
find yourself a new girl

221
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:40,160
and fill up the gap in your heart.

222
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,800
I choose neither.

223
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:44,400
But you can't stay like this, either.

224
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,400
Drinking yourself to oblivion

225
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:47,360
and crying your heart out?

226
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:50,120
When did I cry my heart out?

227
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,640
Then be quick.

228
00:11:53,350 --> 00:11:55,200
Wash your face with water instead of tears,

229
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,640
get changed, and make yourself handsome.

230
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:57,240
Come with me.

231
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,480
Be quick.

232
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,440
Get up.

233
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:03,280
Never mind that bleeding heart.

234
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:06,280
Never mind those teary eyes.

235
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:08,200
Today, let me

236
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,240
have a drink

237
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,600
with you.

238
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:13,000
Go on, wash your face.

239
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,760
What's the plan, the three of you?

240
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:18,400
Here.

241
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:19,240
Drink a can, too.

242
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,560
Hefeweissbier from Wurenbacher.

243
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:21,680
Let's drink together.

244
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,920
I can't drink with you.

245
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:25,600
I still have to keep an eye on the restaurant.

246
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,400
Do you know,

247
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:27,400
Liu?

248
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:29,080
Feng Xi is a woman of profession

249
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:29,800
and responsibility.

250
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:31,440
She is very devoted.

251
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:32,720
Most importantly,

252
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:34,360
she is great at taking care of others.

253
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:36,280
She can take care of people so well

254
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,440
from up to down

255
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,440
and from inside to outside.

256
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:41,200
She's so much better at this than my sis.

257
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,400
I mean it, Feng Xi.

258
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:43,160
I really

259
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:45,360
have to learn it from you.

260
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:47,040
I can't take care of people at all.

261
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:50,080
Am I right, Yu?

262
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:53,200
She's being very honest.

263
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,200
Bao Xue really doesn't know how to take care of others.

264
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:56,760
Feng Xi is so much

265
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:58,200
better than she and her sis in this.

266
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,400
Have you been drinking honey?

267
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:01,800
There's no honey at all.

268
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:03,400
We're just being honest, can't we?

269
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:05,080
I'm just not as clever as you.

270
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,680
If I didn't devote more,

271
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:08,840
clever people like you wouldn't be friends with me, 
 right?

272
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:10,080
Hear, hear.

273
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:12,480
She's also very modest.

274
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,400
Feng Xi.

275
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,520
Yeah.

276
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:16,320
The restaurant totally depends on you.

277
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:17,760
They always tell me that.

278
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:18,680
Right.

279
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:19,280
You're devoted.

280
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:20,280
Cheers.

281
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:21,760
Here's to you.

282
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,400
I'll empty it. Be my guest.

283
00:13:23,400 --> 00:13:24,160
Thanks.

284
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,400
It might work.

285
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:29,280
Did you hear what he said just now?

286
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:30,800
"I'll empty it. Be my guest."

287
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:31,800
Liu,

288
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,200
you're a true man.

