293
00:13:38,680 --> 00:13:39,480
Don't mention him.

294
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,200
Alright, alright.

295
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,000
I won't.

296
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,040
Feng Xi,

297
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,440
what do you

298
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:46,040
think of Liu?

299
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:47,960
He's a good man.

300
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:49,800
Liu,

301
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:51,880
what do you think of Feng Xi?

302
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:53,440
What do you mean?

303
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,240
Are you trying to

304
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,960
make a match between...

305
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,560
Exactly, that's what I mean.

306
00:14:04,560 --> 00:14:06,360
Charity begins at home.

307
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:07,520
Bao Xue.

308
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,800
That's annoying.

309
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:11,720
Just ignore her.

310
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:13,000
She has a thick head.

311
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:14,000
I'll return to work.

312
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:14,560
Wait.

313
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:16,280
You look like such a match when sitting together.

314
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:17,720
It was such a harmonious scene.

315
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:18,760
Come on, stop it.

316
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:20,680
Why are you pulling me?

317
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:22,840
Can you do something reliable?

318
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:24,040
Why am I not reliable?

319
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:25,960
