320
00:14:26,400 --> 00:14:27,320
I told you.

321
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,160
It won't happen.

322
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:28,960
Look at you.

323
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:30,640
Liu,

324
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:32,440
tell me the truth.

325
00:14:33,030 --> 00:14:34,760
Do you think Feng Xi is not good enough for you?

326
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,680
What are you talking about?

327
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:37,960
It's not about

328
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,120
if she's good enough for me.

329
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,360
Forget about it.

330
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:41,480
Just stop it for a while.

331
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:43,120
They don't have feelings for each other.

332
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:43,720
Why do you...

333
