338
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,280
I haven't eaten anything the whole day.

339
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:01,920
Why are you here today?

340
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:04,880
We're helping Liu to get rid of his sorrows.

341
00:15:04,880 --> 00:15:06,760
My sis doesn't know chalk from cheese

342
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:08,440
and did something so outrageous.

343
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,640
I worry that he'd kill himself at home

344
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:12,480
and took him here for emotional treatment.

345
00:15:15,160 --> 00:15:15,920
Whose drink is this?

346
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:17,120
Feng Xi.

347
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,120
But she barely touched it.

348
00:15:18,680 --> 00:15:19,680
Cheers, Liu.

349
00:15:19,680 --> 00:15:20,520
I'm sorry.

350
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,560
A toast to you.

351
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:24,120
From now on,

352
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:27,760
