357
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:34,880
But that's the same with me.

358
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:36,760
You

359
00:15:36,760 --> 00:15:38,360
contributed to us.

360
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:40,000
He is hurt by us.

361
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:40,920
Different reasons,

362
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:42,200
same treatment.

363
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,080
Thanks, Shan.

364
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:48,320
You haven't hurt me.

365
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,880
Let's not talk about the past.

366
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,800
Shan?

367
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:58,120
Liu.

368
00:15:58,350 --> 00:15:58,850
Shan

369
00:15:58,850 --> 00:16:00,020
has wealth, a career,

370
00:16:00,020 --> 00:16:01,440
a good appearance and a fit body.

371
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:02,280
As the saying goes,

372
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:04,490
“A wife three years older than the husband 
 ensures a richer life.”

373
00:16:04,490 --> 00:16:05,640
Shan happens to be single.

374
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:07,080
If you are with Shan, you can save yourself

375
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:09,080
decades of years of hard work earning money.

376
