Shan,

377
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:10,720
don't you like photography?

378
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:13,400
Liu is a senior photographer.

379
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:14,280
He can take photos for you.

380
00:16:14,280 --> 00:16:15,440
Stop it.

381
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,480
Especially...

382
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:20,160
What are you plotting?

383
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:24,240
Do you have nothing else to do when there's not filming?

384
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,660
Right. She really has nothing else to do.

385
00:16:25,660 --> 00:16:26,680
Shan, let me tell you.

386
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:28,040
Before you arrived,

387
00:16:28,040 --> 00:16:29,640
she tried to push Feng Xi to me.

388
00:16:29,640 --> 00:16:31,120
After you arrived,

389
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,680
she tries to push you to me.

390
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:33,640
Liu,

391
00:16:33,640 --> 00:16:35,200
I have realized.

392
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:37,080
There's something wrong with her family gene.

393
00:16:37,280 --> 00:16:38,360
She is the same as her sis.

394
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:39,480
Unreliable.

395
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:41,920
Let me explain it, Shan.

396
00:16:41,920 --> 00:16:43,720
I really did it for your good.

397
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:45,000
Don't you like photographers?

398
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,320
Liu is a photographer. Take photos

399
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:46,920
and I'll help you...

400
00:16:46,920 --> 00:16:47,500
Eat something.

401
00:16:47,500 --> 00:16:48,890
Wait. Which side are you on?

402
00:16:48,890 --> 00:16:50,600
Why do you try to make a match between everyone?

403
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,240
